data.description: Nicely Maintained 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home in Hunters Greene located on a quiet Cul-de-sac. Enter the foyer area which has hardwood floors and flanked to the left you will find a very spacious Living room that will lead you straight through to the dining area. Off the dining area you will find the large eat in kitchen which has tiled floors, granite countertops, large pantry and sliders leading to a large 13 x 18 patio. The back yard is open and of good size for your outdoor entertaining. On the second level you will find a large master bedroom with a walk in closet and a full bath. The other two bedrooms are of good size and you will also find a second floor laundry room for added convenience. This home has newer floor coverings, windows, roof and siding. You will also find the front porch a nice option to enjoy those summer nights. This home is neutral throughout and is awaiting a new owner. Be sure to include this home on your "Must See" List
